  artifact; the throwaway DAST is an unauthenticated loopback spider that does
  not consume it, so these endpoints were not necessarily exercised.
  Authenticated / prod-equivalent endpoint testing remains owner-run.
- **Prod-equivalence: PENDING owner attestation.** The spec was captured from
